{"word":"G4866 - συναθλέω - synathléō - soon-ath-leh'-o - Labour with","slug":"G4866","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συναθλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>synathléō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soon-ath-leh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Labour with"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03BD;&#x03B1;&#x03B8;&#x03BB;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - sunathleo&#x0304;</b> - <i>soon-ath-leh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G118\">G118</a>; to <i>wrestle</i> in company <i>with</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>seek jointly:</i> - labour with, strive together for."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G118\">G118</a>, <a href=\"#/G119\">G119</a>"}]}